    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "man i knew it. i've been feeling this weird pressure in my head whenever i look up at it lately. its like it's tracking my thoughts or something. if those things ARE man-made like u said, how would they even manage to send signals from that far away without us knowing? like, what kind of tech could actually do that?",
